Guest:
  - view public posts and events
  - view clubs profile

Admin:
  - give a User the Student role
  - kick out users
  - view statistics
  - change the clubs responsible

User:
  - view public posts and events
  - comment on PUBLIC posts and events
  
Student:
  - view public and studentsOnly posts and events
  - request to join clubs
  - book PUBLIC and STUDENTS_ONLY events
  - comment on PUBLIC and STUDENTS_ONLY posts and events

ClubsResponsible:
  note: he himself can not be a clubPresident or an assistantMember in any club
  - create clubs and assign the clubPresident
  - change the clubPresident of any club
  - view all posts and events
  - book PUBLIC and STUDENTS_ONLY events
  - manage reservation calendar 
  - hide posts and events

ClubPresident:
  - create and manage the club posts and events
  - assign assistant members
  - accept new members
  - customize assistant members authorities
  - ban out members
  - view members history
  - comment on PUBLIC, STUDENTS_ONLY and PRIVATE posts and events

ClubMember:
  - view PUBLIC, STUDENTS_ONLY and PRIVATE posts and events  
  - comment on PUBLIC, STUDENTS_ONLY and PRIVATE posts and events
  - book an event
